							We believe money should be <span class="glow-purple">understood, mastered</span>, and used to create <span class="glow-gold">freedom</span>. That means clear guidance, powerful tools, and a platform that feels as <span class="glow-cyan">bold</span> as the future it helps shape.
						</p>
						<p class="body-text">
							This is <span class="glow-purple">more than an app</span>. It is a <span class="glow-gold">movement</span> for people who want to build real <span class="glow-cyan">confidence</span>, real <span class="glow-purple">knowledge</span>, and real <span class="glow-gold">momentum</span>.
						</p>
